Package: hamstr
Type: Package
Title: Hierarchical Accumulation Modelling with Stan and R
Version: 0.7.1
Encoding: UTF-8
Authors@R: c(person("Andrew", "Dolman", email = "andrew.dolman@awi.de", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Age-depth sediment accumulation modelling for sediment cores. hamstr
  implements a Bacon-like sediment accumulation or age-depth model,
  similar to that of Blaauw and Christen (2011) <doi:10.1214/ba/1339616472>, but 
  with hierarchically structured multi-resolution discrete sediment sections.
  The Bayesian model is implemented in the Stan probabilistic programming 
  language <https://mc-stan.org/>.
License: GPL-3
